 is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView/update":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView\/update","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"update"}],"title":"update","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"update"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Updates the user location annotation."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview\/update"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView/mapView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview\/mapview","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView\/mapView","abstract":[{"text":"Returns the associated map view.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","title":"mapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"t